{"type": "article", "id": 9832, "title": "Nendo 天然皮革产品", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114437QyCoJmKOfgL7GjPv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t天然皮革会随着时间流逝的转变颜色和感觉，形成个人独一无二的印记。Nendo 从这个角度出发，为皮革制品涂上了无色的 SPF 50 防晒油，在使用中随着时间的推移，皮具会显示出各种不同的图案，而随着更多时间的暴露，标记又会随着整体的剥落全部消失。“Suntan 图案”有条纹，方格，圆点，信封式四种设计，而五款产品分别是文件夹、书皮、名片夹、收纳盒和一款凳子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114434Igb5Sdfq7W6C4TMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70687023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114434RPHLzIlq2wTNkMv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114435zL1jxwERQJAU6OsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071144358GnXQKao4eOPADkm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071144359VtHM0yRZLEYIlTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114436dZAL2D6xhTOnUFw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071144365gpL4VfeRW3EUckd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}